{"words":[{"word":"te","count":4},{"word":"hyvatia","count":3},{"word":"miss","count":3},{"word":"lynae","count":3},{"word":"time","count":3},{"word":"new","count":3},{"word":"professor","count":3},{"word":"institute","count":2},{"word":"wonder","count":2},{"word":"roya","count":2},{"word":"calibrate","count":2},{"word":"data","count":2},{"word":"href","count":2},{"word":"anslem","count":2},{"word":"collective","count":2},{"word":"mornye","count":2},{"word":"lost","count":1},{"word":"control","count":1},{"word":"class","count":1},{"word":"hours","count":1},{"word":"remains","count":1},{"word":"found","count":1},{"word":"making","count":1},{"word":"things","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"fact","count":1},{"word":"footage","count":1},{"word":"avoiding","count":1},{"word":"cameras","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"possible","count":1},{"word":"exoswarm","count":1},{"word":"truly","count":1},{"word":"expand","count":1},{"word":"scope","count":1},{"word":"investigation","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1},{"word":"security","count":1},{"word":"breach","count":1},{"word":"database","count":1},{"word":"compromised","count":1},{"word":"today's","count":1},{"word":"feed","count":1},{"word":"last","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"federation","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"noticed","count":1},{"word":"stay","count":1},{"word":"academy","count":1},{"word":"breaks","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1},{"word":"home","count":1},{"word":"simply","count":1},{"word":"return","count":1},{"word":"partners","count":1},{"word":"calculations","count":1},{"word":"unquestionable","count":1},{"word":"uphold","count":1},{"word":"side","count":1},{"word":"bargain","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"solar","count":1},{"word":"ceremony","count":1},{"word":"goes","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"hitch","count":1},{"word":"believe","count":1},{"word":"counsel","count":1},{"word":"third","count":1},{"word":"person","count":1},{"word":"serve","count":1},{"word":"point","count":1},{"word":"matters","count":1},{"word":"ensuring","count":1},{"word":"calculate","count":1},{"word":"reactor","count":1},{"word":"drive's","count":1},{"word":"launch","count":1},{"word":"sun","count":1},{"word":"importance","count":1},{"word":"process","count":1},{"word":"sincerely","count":1},{"word":"hope","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"trust","count":1},{"word":"shared","count":1},{"word":"achievement","count":1},{"word":"future","count":1},{"word":"lahai-roi","count":1},{"word":"respect","count":1},{"word":"caution","count":1},{"word":"pride","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"past","count":1},{"word":"failures","count":1},{"word":"hold","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"cody","count":1},{"word":"vance","count":1},{"word":"examine","count":1},{"word":"orbital","count":1},{"word":"status","count":1},{"word":"helios","count":1},{"word":"propulsion","count":1},{"word":"system","count":1},{"word":"needs","count":1},{"word":"double-checked","count":1},{"word":"understand","count":1},{"word":"concerns","count":1},{"word":"verge","count":1},{"word":"disaster","count":1},{"word":"sit","count":1},{"word":"watch","count":1},{"word":"happen","count":1},{"word":"decision","count":1},{"word":"supervisor","count":1},{"word":"project","count":1},{"word":"bear","count":1},{"word":"consequences","count":1},{"word":"managed","count":1},{"word":"obtain","count":1},{"word":"wonderful","count":1},{"word":"news","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"prepare","count":1},{"word":"connective","count":1},{"word":"instruments","count":1},{"word":"serious","count":1},{"word":"accusation","count":1},{"word":"tch","count":1},{"word":"lot","count":1},{"word":"assumptions","count":1},{"word":"conjectures","count":1},{"word":"evidence","count":1},{"word":"easily","count":1},{"word":"sue","count":1},{"word":"slander","count":1},{"word":"traitor","count":1},{"word":"manage","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"What were you doing when Hyvatia lost control, Miss Lynae? Why were you at the Institute during class hours?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"No such remains were found, Miss Lynae. Making things up won't help you.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"They didn't. And in fact, you aren't in the footage at all. I wonder what you were doing at that time. Avoiding the cameras, perhaps?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Possible. But only if she and the Exoswarm were truly there.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"We should expand the scope of the investigation. Remember the security breach in the database? There might be more compromised than just today's feed.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"One last thing, Miss Lynae. You're from the New Federation, right?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Nothing. I just noticed you stay at the Academy even during breaks. Never thought of going home?","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Not at all. I simply wonder if you <i>don't want</i> to return.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"The Roya are our partners, Professor.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Their calculations are unquestionable. All we can do is uphold our side of the bargain and make sure the New Solar Ceremony goes off without a hitch.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Well then... I believe counsel from a third person may serve us well at this point.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"What matters now is ensuring that the Institute can calculate and calibrate the Reactor Drive's data in time for the launch of the new sun.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"We all know the importance of <te href=700013>Hyvatia</te> in this process, and I sincerely hope you'll place more trust in it, Anslem.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"This is a shared achievement between the Collective and the Roya, the very future of Lahai-Roi. I respect your caution and the pride you take in your work. But please, don't let past failures hold you back now.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000003},{"text":"Where is Anslem at a time like this?! Who else can calibrate Hyvatia?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"Cody, Vance, examine the orbital status of <te href=700017>Helios</te> again. Also, the propulsion system needs to be double-checked!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"I understand your concerns... but we're on the verge of a disaster. The Collective can't just sit by and watch it happen.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"This is my decision as the supervisor of this project. I will bear the consequences.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"...Professor Mornye?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"Did you just say you managed to obtain the data? Wonderful news. I'll prepare the connective instruments for you—","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"That is a serious accusation, Professor Mornye.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"Tch, that is a lot of assumptions and conjectures. With no evidence, I could easily sue you for slander—","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002},{"text":"(How did that traitor manage to...?!)","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":936000002}]}